verses.text: Behold, bless ye the \+w LORD strong="H3068"\+w**, all ye* servants of the \+w LORD strong="H3068"\+w**, which by night stand in the house of the \+w LORD strong="H3068"\+w**.
Lift up your hands in* the sanctuary, and bless the \+w LORD strong="H3068"\+w**.+ 134.2 the sanctuary: or, holiness*
The \+w LORD strong="H3068"\+w** that made heaven and earth bless thee out of Zion.
